cs.CV, cs.MM, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.CL 

Reasoning: 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with visual attributes and image analysis. 
- cs.MM (Multimedia) is also likely as the paper focuses on fashion images and their organization. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is relevant as the paper proposes an unsupervised approach to learn a style-coherent representation. 
- cs.IR (Information Retrieval) is relevant as the paper discusses the retrieval of fashion images by their style. 
- cs.CL (Computation and Language) is less likely but still possible as the paper uses probabilistic polylingual topic models to discover latent style factors.
